<br>
These can be done by multiple people at once. Nothing despawns.<br>
<br>
Buy 1 Dawnshroud Cider - Vantak Mere sells Dawnshroud Cider for 52pp at loc 830, neg 600 in S.Seru. This is close to the zone-in.<br>
Give cider to Dalini in Netherbian Lair - spawns dorey<br>
Give Dorey 4 bixie crunchies - get bixie charm - he does not despawn.<br>
Bring bixie charm to Torsten in sanctus seru loc neg 988,neg 527, south east praetorium. first floor<br>
- get note <br>
spawn dorey again if necessary, but he should be up - give note - get &quot;Bregun's Directions&quot;<br>
give directions to torsten - get 1st earring<br>
<br>
Euzan Jurek in sanctus seru neg 138 pos 263, north west praetorium. second floor.<br>
say &quot;i want to bring about change&quot; - get replacement records<br>
Find &quot;A file cabinet&quot; on the third floor of the SE praetorium.<br>
give file to file cabinet - need to use sneak or invis tricks - get old records<br>
guard will spawn. kill him. green to 59, max hit of 76. will summon.<br>
give old records to Euzan along with the first earring.<br>
get 2nd earring and a report to start quest 3 <p><center><img src="http://www.sparnak.com/~sparnak/sig1.jpg"></center></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/usenrye.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Senrye</A> at: 5/3/02 2:39:06 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/ucyricusbloodbane.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Cyricus Bloodbane</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Arch Mage</span><br>  Posts: 347<br> <font color=#333333>(5/3/02 5:58 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerequipmentandquests.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=970.topic&index=2>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Earrings of Veracity </span><hr size=1> you don´t need to do the bixie part of the quest...<br>
